        "Params": "{1: '2', 2: '500019', 4: '400'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 47,
        "ActionId": 48,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{1: '1', 2: 'Lee', 3: 'He found this.', 4: '1'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 48,
        "ActionId": 49,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{3: 'The thing placed on the table is an assistance device for remote connections, an exclusive piece of equipment that belongs to Cerberus.'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 49,
        "ActionId": 50,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{2: 'Construct', 3: 'I knew there should be something that could come in handy!', 4: '2'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 50,
        "ActionId": 51,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{2: 'Construct', 3: 'This channel for remote connection with Constructs is exclusive to Cerberus, and its specs are more advanced compared to the standard ones. It\\'s worth a shot!', 4: '2'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 51,
        "ActionId": 52,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{2: 'Construct', 3: 'But I heard that their commandant is pretty much the only one who can establish a remote connection with Cerberus members. Even if we manage to make it work, there\\'s no guarantee that...', 4: '2'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 52,
        "ActionId": 53,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 302,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{2: 'It\\'s fine.', 3: '54'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 53,
        "ActionId": 54,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{3: 'The Construct mumbles something like \"The Gray Raven Commandant is surely a legend.\" His face contorts with frustration as if he is depicting the pain of building a M.I.N.D. connection with some crazy Constructs, all based on the groundless rumors he has heard.'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 54,
        "ActionId": 55,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{3: 'But the imaginary pain apparently has little effect on his work efficiency—he quickly finishes setting up the device.'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 55,
        "ActionId": 56,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{3: 'Lee lets out a quiet sigh.'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 56,
        "ActionId": 57,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{2: 'Lee', 3: 'I\\'ll call Liv over to get you some emergency medical supplies, just in case.', 4: '1'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 57,
        "ActionId": 58,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{2: 'Construct', 3: 'As far as I know, no one has ever built a remote connection with that new frame... You sure about this?', 4: '2'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 58,
        "ActionId": 59,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 302,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{2: 'There will soon be one.', 3: '60'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 59,
        "ActionId": 60,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{2: 'Construct', 3: 'What I mean is, that the new frame has not been fully calibrated for remote connections. It might take you a few attempts before you reach her, and trust me, the process won\\'t be a walk in the park. You gotta be prepared.', 4: '2'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 60,
        "ActionId": 61,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{3: 'From moments of strangeness to sudden startles, and even times when she is seemingly lost in her own thoughts, you have experienced the full spectrum of her emotions.'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 61,
        "ActionId": 62,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{3: 'It\\'s just a change of her frame, but No. 21 is still No. 21.'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 62,
        "ActionId": 63,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
